# feh key configuration.
# Comments start with a # sign, do not use them mid-line.
# Each line must be blank, a comment, or a key definition.
#
# key definition: <action name> <key1> [<key2> [<key3>]]
#
# Each <key> is an X11 keysym (as output by xev) with optional modifier.
# For instance, C-x would be Ctrl+X, or 4-space Mod4+Space
#
# Hint: install `xev` push button to see name
# Hint: to unbind key just don't define a key and list name only
# Hint: Interfering keybindings get listed where at codeblocks where they
# do interfere

# --action to run scripts
action_0    colon Return


# menu / currently not working even when left on default keys
menu_parent h Left
menu_child  l Right
menu_down   j Down
menu_up     k Up
menu_select space Return
# image navigation
next_img j Right space
prev_img k Left BackSpace
# image movement
scroll_up    J C-Up
scroll_down  K C-Down
scroll_left  H C-Left
scroll_right L C-Right
# File deletion
toggle_filenames
remove
delete
